folder: Victory Boulevard & Baron Boulevard, Staten Island, NY
text:
(1)
3842 Victory Boulevard, east side, between Baron Boulevard and Ridgeway Avenue (south of Travis Avenue). Butler's 1853 map designates this old house as a schoolhouse. On the 1899 and 1907 maps it appears as the property of Ridgeway.
May 19, 1932
P. L. Sperr

(2)
Another view of the old school house and adjoining dwellings,
looking north.
May 19, 1932
P. L. Sperr
